{"word":"Abel-Beth-Maachah","slug":"abel-beth-maachah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abel-Beth-Maachah</b> <a href=\"#/H62\">H62</a> <br/> Called also Abel-Maim. A city in the north of Palestine.<br/> Sheba slain in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=22'>2Sa 20:22</a><br/> Taken by Ben-Hadad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=20'>1Ki 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=4'>2Ch 16:4</a><br/> Taken by Tiglath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=29'>2Ki 15:29</a>"}]}